Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.54,0:01:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Ali?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.01,0:01:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,An old man washed up on the seashore!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he'll live.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Ali.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're in a trade port.}{wiki says he lives in ラサール / Rasaaru, but here we hear clearly "basaru" so it's most likely "bazaar port" and not a place name, unless the wiki is wrong and it's just a misreading of Basrah (https://maps.app.goo.gl/p791GP8Nxp45jqgi6)}You're in Rasaar, a port city.{ラ and バ can sound extremely similar. I'm going with Rasaar/ラサール as per JP wiki. A fictional Arabic-sounding place name is more likely than "bazaar"/"Basrah" imo}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky to be alive, grandpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have caused a great deal of trouble for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get better. Just hang in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.39,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, there's no hope anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.02,0:03:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you kids are fond of ships, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.07,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We wish we had a ship to sail on.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become a first-rate sailor.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like my late father before me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.25,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a sailor at about the same age as you are now.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{It was a perilous journey,}My journey was perilous,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.14,0:04:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{but it was a heaven that only the sailors are allowed in.}{??? I assume that riding a ship was heaven, not that he's going to the sailors' heaven now}but it was also blissful in a way\N only sailors can appreciate.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{I longed for sea...}The sea beckoned me...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.57,0:04:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{because it was manly, and full of dreams...}{not like when sleeping but like "ambitions"}with the promise of making every man's dreams come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.91,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.33,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you kids the strangest tale out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.09,0:04:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, \Nin the sky above a southern island...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.56,0:04:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,something miraculous happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.78,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No one had ever seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.41,0:05:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A star fell onto that island,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.92,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,forcing the island to erupt in a bizarre explosion.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.26,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{Its shape changed completely,}Afterwards, the island's coastline became unrecognizable,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.10,0:05:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{and Altaninad turned into a swirling mass of shining stone.}{I assume it's the name of the island and also that they made it up, can't find it anywhere else}and a certain valley on the island was strewn\N with a multitude of dazzling gemstones.{is ある谷などは lmao}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.77,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, they were guarded by terrifying monsters.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{And even to this day...}Even now, those gemstones remain there...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that bum!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you come here every single day?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to get on the ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! You're too scrawny for that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ali. Cheer up.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.79,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, misters! G'day.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, can we talk to the captain?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.72,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, please let us work on this ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.64,0:08:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you kids aren't ready yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't have room for you anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there nothing we can do?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Better give up now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.51,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.43,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Depart!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.12,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, my beloved port.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.58,0:10:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you have any girl here worth pining over.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's harsh.}I'll find one soon enough.{"tsugi wa ne"}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Allah be praised.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.18,0:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to worship none but Allah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.15,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,May our voyage be peaceful.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's empty already.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme dat. I'll go get us some more.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? A cat?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.83,0:11:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{We didn't take any!}{???}Don't you mess with me!{ibaru n'ja nai}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yasim! Come with me! {ヤシム}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.68,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is it? \NI wanna sleep, don't you see?}{unsure, usually this means "why are you acting like a half-asleep idiot" - maybe that's the joke - yashim is half-asleep but he calls the other guy that for seeing things}What's your problem? \NHas the drink gone to your head?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.36,0:11:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, Yasim!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you that brat from before? {Feels more like this sailor is talking to the kid and not the other sailor}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, mister!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.88,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This punk scared me half to death! \NI oughta throw him overboard!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, w-wait! Hold on.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What, there's more of you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is it this time?}What is it, at such a late hour?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.41,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Captain, these punks were hiding inside the cargo.}Captain, these punks were hiding in the cargo hold.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.54,0:12:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Captain, we could toss them overboard as a warning...}{to make a display}Captain, we could toss them overboard\N to teach them a lesson!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.92,0:12:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.38,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, how'd you even get on board?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.26,0:13:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We hid inside a carpet.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.68,0:13:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Resorted to desperate measures, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.23,0:13:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We're sorry, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.95,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You two got me this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.92,0:13:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna train those boys well.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{The beginning's the most important part.}Make sure to show them the ropes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.76,0:13:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.72,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That one got you, Peppi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! No slacking off!{"sabotte ikan da"}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a useless kid you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully how {\i1}I{\i0} do things.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.82,0:15:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't end up like this too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Boatswain Abdullah. {アブダラ}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.50,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Climb using your stomach muscles!}{idk how}Tense your abs while climbing! Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't look down!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sinbad! Calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ali?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a baby whale!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A sawshark!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Abdullah, fetch the harpoons!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.33,0:18:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad, that whale's in danger!{??? isn't that obvious? maybe he says "it's dangerous to be there"?}{nope, he's stating the obvious}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Move aside!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch how it's done!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.77,0:18:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn show-off...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.69,0:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.82,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Nailed it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.91,0:19:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a real smooth move.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My training finally paid off, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.30,0:19:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad you're okay, little whale!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We've arrived at the port of call!{"○○-jima e kita ne"}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.84,0:20:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn to starboard!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.43,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn to starboard!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.06,0:21:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, you called?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.15,0:21:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{The princess is out wandering again.}Apparently the princess sneaked out again.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sire.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.07,0:21:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess is becoming quite a handful.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't handle her anymore, can you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.66,0:21:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sire. Quite so.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.91,0:21:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you still wish to marry her?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.67,0:21:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's another matter...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.64,0:23:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sinbad, hand it over.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.06,0:23:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sing you a much livelier tune!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.36,0:23:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.36,0:23:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean out your ears and listen!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.63,0:24:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And look! An island up ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.28,0:25:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:49.57,0:25:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Vizier?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:52.20,0:25:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found yet another mysterious treasure.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:56.62,0:26:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:01.00,0:26:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:10.09,0:26:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Vizier.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:11.59,0:26:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the magic guitar?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:15.76,0:26:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sire.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:17.81,0:26:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:20.23,0:26:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're lying...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:21.94,0:26:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:24.65,0:26:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They say when you strum it, \N it conjures gold and jewels.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:32.24,0:26:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, play it.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:48.34,0:26:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Vizier, nothing's coming out.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:52.13,0:26:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:53.17,0:26:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,he must be distorting the melody!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:55.84,0:26:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No matter what melody you play, it won't...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:58.93,0:27:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right, it's just an ordinary guitar!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:02.85,0:27:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{Silence! Lie to me and you'll pay for it!}Silence! If you're lying, you'll have to pay dearly!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:06.15,0:27:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, really bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:21.83,0:27:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Vizier!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:24.08,0:27:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't mess with those innocent men.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:26.96,0:27:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,With respect, Princess, \Nyour advice isn't welcome at this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:31.17,0:27:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, Vizier.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:34.17,0:27:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sire!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:35.63,0:27:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll interrogate them at a later time.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.71,0:28:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get moving!{kono}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:10.00,0:28:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! No gawping!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:24.68,0:28:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:29.06,0:28:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.40,0:28:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't find the boy anywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:37.03,0:28:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools! Search every inch!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:15.28,0:29:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuppi! {??? no clue what it is if not the bird's name, but even then can't hear it well; the cat's name was peppi so it makes sense that the other animals' names are similar}{sounds right}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:17.07,0:29:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:24.99,0:29:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kuppi?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:29.54,0:29:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:31.29,0:29:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:42.93,0:29:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. How amusing.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:46.60,0:29:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're all good people, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:50.52,0:29:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.77,0:29:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could sail the high seas with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:53.73,0:29:54.94,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:05.12,0:30:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:08.04,0:30:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you by chance seen a boy here?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:10.54,0:30:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:12.04,0:30:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:14.42,0:30:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If it turns out that you're hiding him...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:27.93,0:30:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:33.60,0:30:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiddo, come on out!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:34.90,0:30:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your hands off me!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:37.90,0:30:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out already, will you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:40.19,0:30:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll talk!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:44.16,0:30:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:46.53,0:30:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:48.41,0:30:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Way down south...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:51.83,0:30:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this strange island.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:54.42,0:30:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:00.38,0:31:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Insolent brat! Get back here!{burei mono-me}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.01,0:31:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's running away! After him!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:06.05,0:31:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you punk!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:07.22,0:31:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:08.43,0:31:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:09.29,0:31:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:12.27,0:31:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:13.18,0:31:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird. Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:14.39,0:31:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That way? Or over here?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:16.19,0:31:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:20.07,0:31:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:23.49,0:31:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold up!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:23.49,0:31:25.41,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:26.91,0:31:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, you little...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:33.72,0:32:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, here we go.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:13.01,0:33:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What could this be? {should we ask what a shaitan statue is doing in sultan's palace?}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:43.04,0:33:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:44.92,0:33:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:59.18,0:34:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What, is that all?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:02.52,0:34:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:05.86,0:34:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:07.65,0:34:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any money!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:55.78,0:34:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kuppi.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:00.70,0:35:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ali?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:03.41,0:35:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use that to help Ali.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:06.88,0:35:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:22.77,0:35:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Let us out already!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:26.85,0:35:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Quiet in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:32.99,0:35:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault, shooting your mouth off.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:42.62,0:35:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to Ali.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:44.83,0:35:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A slippery little fella like him will be just fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:58.18,0:35:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:59.85,0:36:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you, Princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:02.10,0:36:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd give you a reward.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:08.27,0:36:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged, Princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:32.84,0:36:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, quick!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:34.76,0:36:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:37.63,0:36:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There are horses in the courtyard.{"uraniwa", "courtyard" will suffice for CPS}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:56.40,0:36:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:59.91,0:37:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:16.51,0:37:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:20.80,0:37:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!{"tomare"}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:26.68,0:37:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:29.39,0:37:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:31.98,0:37:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:33.23,0:37:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:37.78,0:37:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already time for us to depart.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:05.14,0:38:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:21.57,0:38:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sinbad! Sinbad! Help, Sinbad...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:30.97,0:39:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Good bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:36.85,0:39:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:38.02,0:39:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's flying overhead!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.57,0:39:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,On a magic feather!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:48.95,0:39:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What an insufferable brat.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:54.96,0:39:58.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,And they're all good people, you know? {29:46}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:09.35,0:40:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, I heard you let those sailors escape.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:13.89,0:40:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Father...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:15.52,0:40:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The vizier was furious.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:19.15,0:40:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, honestly, how can you trust a man like him?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:28.39,0:40:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{That was pretty rebellious.}She seems to be in a particularly bad mood.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:38.96,0:40:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:41.63,0:40:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's Ali!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:44.51,0:40:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's back. Had us all worrying, that kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:47.84,0:40:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See? That's how good my training is!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:58.94,0:41:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:00.98,0:41:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:55.16,0:41:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, urgent news!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:58.12,0:42:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess is missing.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:00.04,0:42:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? She's gone?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:02.67,0:42:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What should we do, Vizier?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:05.04,0:42:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, please accept my apologies!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:14.76,0:42:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:19.43,0:42:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Samir! {samiru}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:34.28,0:42:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:36.03,0:42:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty please, take me with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:42.08,0:42:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't send me back, will you?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:09.23,0:43:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}are{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:14.28,0:43:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:20.04,0:43:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:33.63,0:43:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Vizier, what's wrong? \NYou look irritated.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:37.26,0:43:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like my style? Lovely, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:39.81,0:43:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I have no use for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:46.02,0:43:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Each and every last one of them...
Dialogue: 10,0:44:00.45,0:44:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're the one I need.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:08.50,0:44:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my servant from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:11.21,0:44:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name shall be... Hell Bat!{Note: ヘルバット, I have a creeping suspicion this is Hell Bat lmao. Leaving the final choice to the editor.}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:17.59,0:44:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:21.14,0:44:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll follow the Princess and \Nkeep an eye on her. Understood?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:26.02,0:44:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:41.58,0:44:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Allah is great.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:45.79,0:44:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of Allah the eternal, \Nmay today's voyage be safe and peaceful.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:56.15,0:44:57.42,Top,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:09.85,0:45:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, man your stations!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:21.16,0:45:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They say if you depart from this sea \Nand sail all the way south,
Dialogue: 10,0:45:26.20,0:45:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a beautiful five-colored island. {五色に輝く宝石の島}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:29.33,0:45:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious fruit, cool springs...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:33.67,0:45:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange flowers and birds, and giant diamonds.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:39.05,0:45:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we can't make detours.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:42.22,0:45:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:45.81,0:45:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:15.50,0:46:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to change course!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:22.59,0:46:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, where are we going?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:25.35,0:46:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To Treasure Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:28.31,0:46:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to starboard!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:14.94,0:47:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali, go have fun with them too.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:18.69,0:47:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it better here.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:25.74,0:47:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, may I join you guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:44.26,0:47:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{Too bad. I'm not good with royalty.}{lit: bad with princesses - w/e he means}See, I'm not used to speaking with royals.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:53.02,0:47:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone seem to shun me? {wtf happened to her voice lol}
Dialogue: 10,0:48:01.94,0:48:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're so different.{funny/strange - probably means "they're not used to socializing with someone like you"}{yep}
Dialogue: 10,0:48:05.95,0:48:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:19.46,0:48:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're back, Hell Bat?
Dialogue: 10,0:48:27.30,0:48:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The Princess in on the {\i1}Boldar{\i0}? {name of that ship, boruda - could as well be "boulder", perhaps we could use a help of someone fluent in arabic and their names here... renascent's timezone is one hour ahead of mine, perhaps he knows something?}
Dialogue: 10,0:48:34.10,0:48:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A Treasure Island to the south?
Dialogue: 10,0:48:37.56,0:48:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:40.44,0:48:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, we've picked up the Princess's trail.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:44.65,0:48:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you, really? So, where is she?
Dialogue: 10,0:48:49.24,0:48:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, I regret to inform you... \NShe's on a ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:52.87,0:48:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are you waiting for? \NGo and bring her back right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:09.55,0:49:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali! Hurry and get down!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:26.61,0:49:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Furl the sails!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:41.12,0:49:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:49:42.29,0:49:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The rope is stuck!{hikkakatta n'da yo}
Dialogue: 10,0:49:47.05,0:49:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 10,0:49:47.76,0:49:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me with this one!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:01.26,0:50:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't make it in time!{maniawan}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:02.56,0:50:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now's our chance!{yoshi, ima ikou}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:04.15,0:50:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A wave is coming!{kuru wa}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:11.78,0:50:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Furl the sails already!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:14.03,0:50:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more we can do!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:16.49,0:50:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:18.37,0:50:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, please take over!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:20.08,0:50:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:23.12,0:50:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it over!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:34.89,0:50:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Samir!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:42.85,0:50:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:44.69,0:50:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:46.90,0:50:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's gonna capsize!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:55.53,0:50:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali! Give me your sword!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:57.95,0:50:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:06.29,0:51:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:07.67,0:51:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight, Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:14.72,0:51:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:15.47,0:51:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:17.60,0:51:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look down!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:19.81,0:51:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:24.81,0:51:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear out! {/Timber! }
Dialogue: 10,0:51:45.75,0:51:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you see the {\i1}Boldar{\i0} yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:48.21,0:51:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir! Nothing yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:04.82,0:52:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that little whale again! {funny trivia from wiki: Regarding the pet that would ride on Sinbad's ship, Tezuka suggested a kitten, while Kita suggested a baby whale . [ 6 ] Tezuka was surprised by the idea but drew a storyboard accordingly, but Toei Animation rejected it, saying, "There's no way a whale could ride on a ship. " [ 5 ]}
Dialogue: 10,0:52:16.74,0:52:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You doing good?
Dialogue: 10,0:52:24.12,0:52:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Peppi.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:26.12,0:52:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad to have a souvenir?
Dialogue: 10,0:52:34.80,0:52:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Whale, it's time for you to go home.\NYour mom's waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:08.46,0:53:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! Kuppi!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:12.21,0:53:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to see you here!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:14.96,0:53:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali, look at the sky ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:20.34,0:53:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful...
Dialogue: 10,0:55:07.66,0:55:15.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,Mother, I'm sorry for worrying you. \NBut I'm really happy now! {/Samir }
Dialogue: 10,0:55:16.33,0:55:20.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,Traveling by ship is wonderful, \Nand I've made such lovely friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:23.63,0:55:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't believe that girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:25.55,0:55:28.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,But you know, we got caught \Nin a terrible storm the other day!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:28.81,0:55:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A storm?!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:30.60,0:55:34.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,But it's fine. Sinbad saved us all.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:34.85,0:55:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad did?
Dialogue: 10,0:55:37.48,0:55:41.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,But I have to admit... \NI'm beginning to miss Father by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:43.42,0:56:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So damn hot out here, Yasim.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:49.39,0:56:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is life, man.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:51.93,0:56:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're low on water too.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:55.06,0:56:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope we get a squall soon, right, Captain?
Dialogue: 10,0:56:58.02,0:57:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:01.19,0:57:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Sinbad, have some water.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:03.98,0:57:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:07.45,0:57:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Princess Samir. {idk why he's so shocked... that she spared some of her own supply for him?}
Dialogue: 10,0:57:30.93,0:57:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My! What's wrong, Peppi?
Dialogue: 10,0:58:15.76,0:58:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency! Hell Bat's back!
Dialogue: 10,0:58:24.40,0:58:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hell Bat, I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:34.07,0:58:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Don't slack on the surveillance.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:37.91,0:58:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Sinbad.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:40.33,0:58:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency, at last we'll get \Nboth the princess and the treasure!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:00.18,0:59:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, the sky looks strange.{was: is acting}
Dialogue: 10,0:59:05.23,0:59:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, the color of the sea is changing!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:12.86,0:59:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:59:14.49,0:59:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's odd. It's stuck.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:23.09,0:59:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, this is bad! \NSomething huge is down there!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:52.49,0:59:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:55.11,0:59:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did we veer off course?
Dialogue: 10,0:59:58.99,1:00:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea is so strange here, right, Sinbad?
Dialogue: 10,1:00:02.58,1:00:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the "Sea of Demons" I've heard about.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:07.00,1:00:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like...
Dialogue: 10,1:00:08.84,1:00:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we aren't getting out of here alive!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:12.13,1:00:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 10,1:00:16.30,1:00:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:47.04,1:00:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{C-Captain, the ghosts...}C-Captain, that's a ghost...
Dialogue: 10,1:00:49.54,1:00:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's the ghosts, Captain!}A ghost ship!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:15.09,1:02:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is bad.
Dialogue: 10,1:02:38.19,1:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's moving!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:42.61,1:02:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:44.74,1:02:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, man your positions!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:04.70,1:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Whale! You came to help us?
Dialogue: 10,1:03:13.98,1:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:16.23,1:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:23.82,1:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency! \NI see a small boat dead ahead of us!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:30.91,1:03:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay! Ready the spears and stay alert!}Okay! Keep it in sight at all times!{見張り}
Dialogue: 10,1:03:34.00,1:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:36.17,1:03:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, fog's rolling in.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:43.17,1:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is some thick fog.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:47.85,1:03:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A very unusual fog, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:50.14,1:03:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Keep your eyes open.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:52.39,1:03:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing anymore.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:55.77,1:03:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come on down.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:59.07,1:04:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,1:04:12.62,1:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:33.06,1:04:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the island, right, Captain?
Dialogue: 10,1:04:35.56,1:04:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... probably.
Dialogue: 10,1:04:41.44,1:04:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what an island!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:44.44,1:04:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:46.86,1:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{Lower the sails!}Drop the anchor!{碇}
Dialogue: 10,1:04:56.83,1:05:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm counting on you people.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:00.67,1:05:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,1:05:15.39,1:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come back with some rare souvenirs, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:21.90,1:05:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me with you!
Dialogue: 10,1:05:31.28,1:05:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. You're staying with me.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:46.59,1:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Treasure Island?
Dialogue: 10,1:05:49.30,1:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it, Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:05:52.43,1:05:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find something incredible on this island.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:59.60,1:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What a creepy bird!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:01.81,1:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:26.13,1:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Samir!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:27.76,1:06:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:28.96,1:06:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:30.47,1:06:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:27.02,1:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:30.36,1:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:35.41,1:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Samir!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:37.70,1:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali!
Dialogue: 10,1:08:07.23,1:08:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{I could live with this!}How refreshing!{いける/tastes well}
Dialogue: 10,1:08:09.32,1:08:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me drink some too!
Dialogue: 10,1:08:19.87,1:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasim! Help me!
Dialogue: 10,1:08:41.89,1:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure Island, my foot.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:43.85,1:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:04.11,1:11:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go on...
Dialogue: 10,1:11:08.16,1:11:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ali, hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:15.17,1:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:16.54,1:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you find them, \Nkill them on the spot.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:18.41,1:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:26.68,1:11:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Samir!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:33.06,1:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:42.65,1:11:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:46.41,1:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:01.46,1:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them be! We need to hurry!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:47.34,1:12:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nuisance!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:56.94,1:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:07.28,1:13:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:10.03,1:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the five-colored gemstones \Nthe old man talked about!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:14.66,1:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali, more importantly, \Nwe have to find Sinbad now.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:17.96,1:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:19.33,1:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:21.46,1:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad...
Dialogue: 10,1:13:24.25,1:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{Say, fancy place to meet again, isn't it?}Princess! We've crossed paths again \Nin such a mysterious place.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:28.51,1:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from the princess?!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:32.60,1:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:35.39,1:13:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:41.98,1:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:44.19,1:13:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:46.19,1:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:48.57,1:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:49.53,1:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:51.41,1:13:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali, take the princess and get out of here!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:53.53,1:13:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After them, men!{"hayaku oe"}
Dialogue: 10,1:14:04.75,1:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:23.06,1:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's the princess!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:30.45,1:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:32.03,1:14:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop struggling, you wench!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:32.03,1:14:34.53,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:34.53,1:14:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:35.99,1:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught you, kiddo!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:37.33,1:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sinbad! We're h—
Dialogue: 10,1:14:37.62,1:14:38.58,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ali!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:39.20,1:14:40.04,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:40.04,1:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:06.58,1:16:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You lot, stuff the gems in the bags, now!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:14.84,1:16:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Samir!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:16.68,1:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:36.49,1:16:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is magnificent.
Dialogue: 10,1:17:14.86,1:17:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry back to the ship!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:58.74,1:18:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Samir! Ali!
Dialogue: 10,1:18:08.77,1:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 10,1:18:39.07,1:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 10,1:18:47.04,1:18:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad! Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:18:49.96,1:18:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Samir! Ali!
Dialogue: 10,1:18:53.33,1:18:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinbad!
Dialogue: 10,1:19:01.97,1:19:04.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,Merciful God of Allah,
Dialogue: 10,1:19:05.51,1:19:09.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,I pray that you may save their lives.
Dialogue: 10,1:20:29.01,1:20:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I've found a treasure \Nfar greater than any jewel.
Dialogue: 10,1:20:33.31,1:20:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? And what's that?
Dialogue: 10,1:20:35.94,1:20:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Samir... it's you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.59,0:07:33.78,Song,,0,0,0,,Our ship's hold is full
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.78,0:07:40.34,Song,,0,0,0,,Of heavy goods
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.70,0:07:53.10,Song,,0,0,0,,Our ship's hold is full
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.10,0:07:59.56,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Of heavy goods
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.14,0:08:59.23,Song,,0,0,0,,{ikari wo agero, tomozuna wo shimero, saraba furusato no minato yo misaki yo, fune wa yuku shibuki wo agete, saraba natsukashii yama yo nagisa yo}Raise the anchor, reel in the mooring lines
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.23,0:09:07.61,Song,,0,0,0,,Good bye, harbors and capes of my homeland
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.61,0:09:15.45,Song,,0,0,0,,As our ship departs, it leaves a foamy wake
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.45,0:09:23.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Good bye, my dear mountains and shores
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.42,0:09:31.43,Song,,0,0,0,,Raise the anchor, reel in the mooring lines
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.43,0:09:39.39,Song,,0,0,0,,Good bye, harbors and capes of my homeland
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.39,0:09:47.40,Song,,0,0,0,,As our ship departs, it leaves a foamy wake
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.40,0:09:57.12,Song,,0,0,0,,Good bye, my dear mountains and shores
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.55,0:16:31.39,Song,,0,0,0,,Deep beneath this sea {song is  行こうよみんなのうた, still no trace of lyrics}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.89,0:16:37.60,Song,,0,0,0,,Mysteries await
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.23,0:16:44.18,Song,,0,0,0,,Under these waves
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.18,0:16:49.91,Song,,0,0,0,,Our dreams are hiding
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.91,0:16:56.20,Song,,0,0,0,,So let's go, everyone
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.20,0:17:03.38,Song,,0,0,0,,So let's go, everyone
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.38,0:17:09.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Enveloped by moonlight
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.38,0:17:18.81,Song,,0,0,0,,Into the shadows of the stars
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.33,0:20:43.81,Song,,0,0,0,,I am lonely, all on my own {song of the lonely princess (ひとりぼっちの姫のうた)}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.81,0:20:58.03,Song,,0,0,0,,My five-colored castle and lovely gardens
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.03,0:21:12.29,Song,,0,0,0,,{are all locked away in gray darkness.}Are enveloped in deep darkness
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.29,0:21:19.01,Song,,0,0,0,,My heart
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.47,0:21:28.06,Song,,0,0,0,,Is lost in thick fog...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.79,0:22:45.80,Song,,0,0,0,,Long ago, a Turkish king played his flute and said {Toruko no Ou-sama no Uta }
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.80,0:22:53.81,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of women, tired of feasts
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.81,0:23:01.82,Song,,0,0,0,,What I want is a splendid robe no one else has {kimono}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.36,0:23:09.53,Song,,0,0,0,,{With those words, he told his vassals to come closer.}And then he invited his servant girls to come closer{Note: 近う寄れ is how a lord would make a pass on women of lower social status}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.87,0:23:18.96,Song,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no! No, no, no, no, no, no! \NYou may come closer!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.12,0:24:00.25,Song,,0,0,0,,Now then, this guitar is so wondrous, and I'm a sailor!{Fushigi na Guitar no Uta}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.25,0:24:06.63,Song,,0,0,0,,One day I was rowing my little boat, \Nrowing and rowing across the sea
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.89,0:24:19.77,Song,,0,0,0,,I dropped anchor with a clank, but surprise!\NIt wasn't an island at all, but a giant whale!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.77,0:24:25.94,Song,,0,0,0,,It tossed me way up high, then swallowed me whole
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.40,0:24:29.61,Song,,0,0,0,,But I managed to come back alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:29.61,0:24:36.41,Song,,0,0,0,,And from that whale's insides, I brought out this guitar
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.41,0:24:43.00,Song,,0,0,0,,The very instant you pluck a string,\N gold, silver, and diamonds appear
Dialogue: 10,0:24:43.00,0:24:51.59,Song,,0,0,0,,What a wondrous guitar this is! \NSuch a lovely guitar!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:58.71,0:47:02.59,Song,,0,0,0,,We'll be jolly on our journey!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:02.59,0:47:06.80,Song,,0,0,0,,We'll be tipsy when we set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:29.53,0:47:33.46,Song,,0,0,0,,We'll be jolly on our journey!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:33.46,0:47:37.95,Song,,0,0,0,,We'll be tipsy when we set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:00.58,0:48:04.40,Song,,0,0,0,,We'll be jolly on our journey!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:04.40,0:48:08.03,Song,,0,0,0,,We'll be tipsy when we set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:19.80,0:53:35.07,Song,,0,0,0,,O blue memories, O distant dreams!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:35.07,0:53:52.83,Song,,0,0,0,,{it's the garden of my heart is clearing up.}The fog that enveloped my heart is slowly clearing
Dialogue: 10,0:55:48.62,0:55:57.25,Song,,0,0,0,,Beneath that sky lies happiness abounding
Dialogue: 10,0:55:57.67,0:56:06.05,Song,,0,0,0,,Boundless hope can be found beyond those clouds
Dialogue: 10,0:56:06.05,0:56:15.77,Song,,0,0,0,,So let's go, everyone! Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:15.77,0:56:28.62,Song,,0,0,0,,Beneath that sky, past those clouds
